{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>RedAudio Network</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #a52a2a; /* Brownish-red */\n            --secondary-color: #dcdcdc; /* Light gray */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, #8b0000 100%);\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .scroll-indicator {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 20px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            animation: bounce 2s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes bounce {\n            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {\n                transform: translate(-50%, 0);\n            }\n            40% {\n                transform: translate(-50%, -20px);\n            }\n            60% {\n                transform: translate(-50%, -10px);\n            }\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: #2a2a2a;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #8b0000; /* Darker red on hover */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #111;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: #8b0000;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero-content h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero-content p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1>RedAudio Network</h1>\n            <p>Immerse yourself in compelling stories and insightful conversations. Discover your next favorite podcast.</p>\n            <a href=\"#podcasts\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Podcasts</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"scroll-indicator\">\u25bc</div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"podcasts\">\n            <h2>Our Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/a52a2a/ffffff?text=Podcast+1\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 1\">\n                    <h3>The Crimson Chronicle</h3>\n                    <p>Deep dives into historical mysteries, presented with a modern edge.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/8b0000/ffffff?text=Podcast+2\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 2\">\n                    <h3>Sonic Spectrum</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the diverse world of music, from indie gems to chart-toppers.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/dc143c/ffffff?text=Podcast+3\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 3\">\n                    <h3>The Urban Canvas</h3>\n                    <p>Interviews with artists, designers, and innovators shaping our cities.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/280x200/b22222/ffffff?text=Podcast+4\" alt=\"Podcast Cover 4\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Compass</h3>\n                    <p>Travel narratives and adventure stories from around the globe.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About RedAudio</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;\">RedAudio is dedicated to producing high-quality audio content that educates, entertains, and inspires. We believe in the power of storytelling to connect people and foster understanding. Our network features a curated selection of podcasts spanning various genres, all brought to you with passion and professionalism.</p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 RedAudio Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Follow us on <a href=\"#\">X</a> | <a href=\"#\">Instagram</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-next-section behavior\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}